    "h, i TMZ sensitivity of RAD18 +/+ and RAD18 -/-U373 cells cultured on viable organo-type brain slice explants.",
    "The middle panel shows representative bioluminescence images of firefly luciferase-expressing U373 RAD18 +/+ and RAD18 -/-cells cultured on brain slices and treated with indicated concentrations of TMZ for 4 days.",
